  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/5a233b14f26718b1efdb2114318a7dba.poster.avif?t=1771826609\" width=800 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/5a233b14f26718b1efdb2114318a7dba.webm?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/5a233b14f26718b1efdb2114318a7dba.mp4?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You've lost your memories. The nightmares are waiting. And the girls? They're counting on you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gray Haven is a yuri action RPG where you explore twisted nightmares, rescue lost girls, and build a sanctuary to call your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With fluid controls and hard-hitting combat, every fight plays out exactly the way you want it to.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/a4178e71f9d3b71a56ffbde03f3da01b.poster.avif?t=1771826609\" width=800 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/a4178e71f9d3b71a56ffbde03f3da01b.webm?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/a4178e71f9d3b71a56ffbde03f3da01b.mp4?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each girl carries memories she can't recover alone — and secrets she's never told anyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save them from the nightmare. Earn their trust. And they'll give you everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 300 voiced lines recorded by professional voice actors bring every moment to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/21fbf1cbdb92327840e0bc90d1371540.poster.avif?t=1771826609\" width=800 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/21fbf1cbdb92327840e0bc90d1371540.webm?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/21fbf1cbdb92327840e0bc90d1371540.mp4?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The nightmares are brutal — grotesque monsters, deadly traps, and horrors that don't stop coming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But so are you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master fluid, instantly responsive controls and unleash any playstyle you can imagine — guns, gauntlets, greatswords, katanas, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/3026b1d966c25a630a1ed11b5c96d84b.avif?t=1771826609\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras_big/3026b1d966c25a630a1ed11b5c96d84b.avif?t=1771826609 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the fighting's done, Gray Haven is yours to shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack towers of bones. Plant flower gardens. Build the sanctuary — or the nightmare — that only you could create.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This world belongs to you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/5a233b14f26718b1efdb2114318a7dba.poster.avif?t=1771826609\" width=800 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/5a233b14f26718b1efdb2114318a7dba.webm?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/5a233b14f26718b1efdb2114318a7dba.mp4?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You've lost your memories. The nightmares are waiting. And the girls? They're counting on you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gray Haven is a yuri action RPG where you explore twisted nightmares, rescue lost girls, and build a sanctuary to call your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With fluid controls and hard-hitting combat, every fight plays out exactly the way you want it to.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/a4178e71f9d3b71a56ffbde03f3da01b.poster.avif?t=1771826609\" width=800 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/a4178e71f9d3b71a56ffbde03f3da01b.webm?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/a4178e71f9d3b71a56ffbde03f3da01b.mp4?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each girl carries memories she can't recover alone — and secrets she's never told anyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save them from the nightmare. Earn their trust. And they'll give you everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 300 voiced lines recorded by professional voice actors bring every moment to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/21fbf1cbdb92327840e0bc90d1371540.poster.avif?t=1771826609\" width=800 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/21fbf1cbdb92327840e0bc90d1371540.webm?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/21fbf1cbdb92327840e0bc90d1371540.mp4?t=1771826609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The nightmares are brutal — grotesque monsters, deadly traps, and horrors that don't stop coming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But so are you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master fluid, instantly responsive controls and unleash any playstyle you can imagine — guns, gauntlets, greatswords, katanas, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras/3026b1d966c25a630a1ed11b5c96d84b.avif?t=1771826609\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314650/extras_big/3026b1d966c25a630a1ed11b5c96d84b.avif?t=1771826609 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the fighting's done, Gray Haven is yours to shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack towers of bones. Plant flower gardens. Build the sanctuary — or the nightmare — that only you could create.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This world belongs to you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
